name: How can Digital Palau best serve Zuzalu-alike communities? by Elaine
description:
Pacific islands are going through challenges and transformations. We want to gather community input on how we should do so.

What legal regulations would a Zuzaluan like in a Palau charter zone?

How can Palau support a digital-nomadic, co-living centric innovation community in terms of infrastructure and how can such community give back to Palau?

Casual breakout session with Taiwan pinapple cakes and green tea. 


Hosted by Elaine
